"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?28/45/29394?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Down syndrome (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/7/2161?source=see_link\">",
